## 3. Typography

**Font stack:**
```css
--font-sans: 'Inter', ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif;
--font-mono: 'JetBrains Mono', ui-monospace, monospace;
```

Load both via Google Fonts or self-host in `/public/fonts/`.

### Type Scale

| Token | Size | Line height | Weight | Usage |
|-------|------|------------|--------|-------|
| `text-xs` | 12px | 16px | 400 | Labels, badges, timestamps |
| `text-sm` | 14px | 20px | 400 | Body secondary, descriptions |
| `text-base` | 16px | 24px | 400 | Body primary, task titles |
| `text-lg` | 18px | 28px | 500 | Section headings in panels |
| `text-xl` | 20px | 28px | 600 | Page titles (Today, Inbox) |
| `text-2xl` | 24px | 32px | 700 | Auth page headlines |
| `text-3xl` | 30px | 36px | 700 | Onboarding hero |

### Text Colour Rules
- Primary content: `--text-primary`
- Supporting metadata (dates, counts): `--text-secondary`
- Placeholder text in inputs: `--text-disabled`
- Completed task titles: `--text-secondary` + `line-through`

