## 4. Spacing & Layout Grid

Base unit: **4px**. All margins, paddings, and gaps are multiples of 4.

```
4px  → xs  (tight inline gaps)
8px  → sm  (icon-to-label gaps, inner cell padding)
12px → md- (compact rows)
16px → md  (standard section padding)
20px → lg- (card padding)
24px → lg  (section gap)
32px → xl  (major section separation)
48px → 2xl (page-level top padding)
```

### App Shell Dimensions

| Region | Width / Height |
|--------|--------------|
| Sidebar (desktop) | 240px fixed |
| Sidebar (collapsed) | 56px (icons only) |
| Task list column | Fluid (fills remaining space) |
| Task detail panel | 380px fixed, right side |
| Header height | 56px |
| Mobile nav height | 64px |
| Modal max-width | 560px |
| Toast width | 360px |

