## 8. Interaction & Motion

All animations use **Framer Motion**. Keep durations short — this is a productivity tool, not a portfolio site.

### Timing Reference

| Interaction | Duration | Easing |
|------------|---------|--------|
| Button hover/active | 100ms | ease-out |
| Row hover highlight | 120ms | ease-out |
| Task complete (fade + strikethrough) | 300ms | ease-in-out |
| Modal open | 200ms | ease-out |
| Modal close | 150ms | ease-in |
| Detail panel slide in (desktop) | 250ms | ease-out |
| Sheet slide up (mobile) | 300ms | spring (stiffness 400, damping 40) |
| Sidebar collapse/expand | 200ms | ease-in-out |
| Toast slide in | 250ms | spring |
| Toast slide out | 200ms | ease-in |
| Skeleton shimmer | 1500ms | linear, infinite |
| Drag overlay lift | 150ms | ease-out (scale 1.02, slight shadow) |
| Confetti (onboarding) | 2500ms | physics |

### Key Micro-interactions

**Task completion:**
1. User clicks checkbox
2. Checkbox immediately shows checkmark (optimistic)
3. Title gets `line-through` and fades to `text-secondary` over 300ms
4. Task slides slightly down and fades out of active list after 800ms delay (so user can see it happened)
5. Success toast: "Task completed ✓  [Undo]"

**Task creation (quick-add):**
1. Input expands with a subtle height animation
2. New task row appears at top of list with a brief green flash (`bg-success-light`)
3. Input clears, ready for next task

**Drag and drop:**
1. On drag start: picked-up row becomes a translucent overlay; a placeholder gap remains in list
2. While dragging: other rows slide apart smoothly to indicate drop position
3. On drop: row snaps into position; order saved immediately (optimistic, background API call)
4. On drag fail (network error): row snaps back with shake animation + toast

**Notifications badge:**
- New notification: bell icon does a brief `ring` rotate animation (15deg left-right, 3 times)
- Badge count increments with a small scale-up pop

