## 14. Error States

### Field-Level Validation (Forms)
- Error message appears below the input in `text-danger text-sm`
- Input border changes to `border-danger`
- Error icon (AlertCircle) inline at right of input
- Trigger: on blur (not on keystroke)

### API Error Toast
- Toast type: destructive (red)
- Message: human-readable (not raw error codes)
- "Retry" action where applicable
- Auto-dismisses after 6 seconds (longer than success toasts)

### Full-Page Error (unexpected crash)
- React Error Boundary catches render errors
- Shows a centered error card: "Something went wrong" + "Try refreshing the page" button
- Reports error to Sentry automatically

### Network Offline Banner
- A yellow top banner slides down: "You're offline. Changes will sync when you reconnect."
- Banner disappears automatically when connection is restored
- Toast confirms: "Back online. Syncing…"

